snippet.textDisplay: Your going to need a 1 inch long anvil impact gun and I think a 33 mm socket deep well for that 1 inch drive impact also that DD will do what you need there is honestly no reason to turbo it also dont walk under the boom when the hydraulics are excited and if its leaking you can lose the pressure in the system and it will come down fast and hurt you guys and quite possibly kill you and for services on it as in greasing the  cylinders and everything else I would hit it once a month and for oil change intervals if yall dont use it on a daily basis maybe once a week change engine oil every 6 months if you use it daily for multiple hours a day change every 3 months and the diff oil I'd change twice a year if you use it every day and the fuel filters change every 3 months regardless because of debris and contamination in the fuel but other then that it looks like it will be a good easy and quick project for yall that will do everything yall need
